# Authorization Page

## Layout
- Standalone full-screen (NO sidebar, NO header)
- Top-level route outside `AppShell`
- Page wrapper: `flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-[#f5f9fe] p-6`

## Card
- `bg-white w-[620px] rounded-[4px] overflow-hidden`

## Branded Header
- `bg-[#004299]`
- White Paytm logo top-left
- `gap-[28px]` between logo and title+email group
- Title+email grouped with `gap-3`
- App name highlighted in `text-[#00b8f5]`

## Permission Icons
- Container: `bg-[#fafafa]` (neutral) — NOT `bg-[#e0f5fd]`

## Checkbox Consent
- No background card
- `items-center` alignment
- Checkbox + text inline with `gap-3`
- Text: `text-[12px] leading-[20px]`

## Disclaimer
- `gap-0` between lines
- First line: `text-[12px]`
- Second line: `text-[10px]`

## Buttons
- Cancel (Medium emphasis) and Authorize (High emphasis)
- Both `flex-1` for equal width

## Footer Bar
- Sky blue `#00b8f5` (8px) + Navy `#012a72` (8px) strip at bottom
